{"tid":2492351,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論]譚仔國際上市","createTime":"2021-04-17T05:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T06:43:16.000Z","uid":395580,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0e0f2807f051c40bb52552fe2a39a2bac790c4","tid":2492351,"uid":395580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"食過唔同鋪頭既米線，亦都幾鐘意食米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但譚仔既米線大不如前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫個麻辣一啲都無麻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反仲記得一開始譚仔開業個陣麻味勁香，食到上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但宜家就黎可以歸類為劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由其係譚仔三哥，夠膽死個面餅都未化就拎上枱俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n湯底淡過船灣淡水湖啲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家都小食譚仔，話知佢沖出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉場試下雲貴香，臻味等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c64de46a8179b68308eaaa65d484f9a485e25b","tid":2492351,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"要撐住股價所以要日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9da21af95aca176d3d3c384e33af3023c45728d","tid":2492351,"uid":254453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"明明冇咩特別但又成日掛住，佢個味精湯真係好古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c7804382049888a873030ff69f5ef71f110972","tid":2492351,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"香港版MCD"},{"pid":"77592f56620ea4e2ed15d9df987528c